<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1><%= title %> API Documentation</h1>
    <span class="subLinks">[ github: <a href="https://git.generalassemb.ly/GainorB/Tweedr">https://git.generalassemb.ly/GainorB/Tweedr</a> | live: <a href=""></a> ]</span><br>
    No authentication is required to access this API. All resources are fully open and available.
    <ul>
    <li>There is, however, a daily rate limit of 100 requests per resource per IP address. This is to stop our database from falling over under heavy load.</li>
    <li>By using, our API you agree to our Terms of Service.</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>GET ALL TWEEDS</h3>
    <div class="getDiv"><span class="larger"><span class="get">GET</span> https://tweedrapp.herokuapp.com/<span class="get">getTweeds</span></span></div>
    <h3>HOW TO CREATE A TWEED</h3>
    <div class="createDiv"><span class="larger"><span class="create">POST</span> https://tweedrapp.herokuapp.com/<span class="create">createTweed</span></span></div>
    <h5>JSON FORMAT</h5>
    <div class="createDiv"><small>{ <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"post" : "content goes here"<br> }</small></div>
    <h5>SUCCESS RESPONSE</h5>
    <div class="successDiv">
         <small>{ <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"Success" : "Tweed Created."<br> }</small></div>
    <h5>ERROR RESPONSE</h5>
    <div class="errorDiv">
         <small>{ <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"Error" : "Tweed Not Created. Try Again."<br> }</small></div>
    <h5>STATUS CODES</h5>
    <div class="statusDiv"><small><p><span class="get">200 OK:</span> The request has completed successfully.</p>
         <p><span class="get">201 Created:</span> The request has been fulfilled, resulting in the creation of a new resource.</p>
         <p><span class="error">400 Bad Request:</span> Invalid submission.</p>
         <p><span class="error">401 Unauthorized:</span> The user is not authorized.</p>
         <p><span class="error">404 Page Not Found:</span> The requested page doesn't exist.</p>
         <p><span class="error">500 Internal Server Error:</span> Internal server exception. The request didn't succeed.</p></small></div>
  </body>
</html>
